            <div class="space-y-6 lg:space-y-8">
                <div class="space-y-4">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold font-display tracking-tight">The Technical <span class="text-gradient">Edge</span></h2>
                    <div class="h-1.5 w-20 bg-primary-500 rounded-full"></div>
                </div>

                <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-slate-300 leading-relaxed max-w-lg">

                
                    I offer a rare combination of deep <strong>data engineering</strong> and <strong>information science</strong> expertise.   
                    I build <strong>open-source</strong> tools that power modern data management platforms, 
                    collaborate with agencies that lead <strong>standards and best practices</strong>,
                    and support data stewards throughout their <strong>digital transformation</strong> journey, 
                    to ensure high-value data is equally accessible to both <strong>humans and machines</strong>.
                </p>

                <div class="pt-2">
                    <a href="/assets/docs/HeusPascal.pdf" download class="inline-flex items-center space-x-2 glass px-6 py-3 rounded-xl font-bold hover:bg-white/10 transition-all border-white/10 text-sm w-full sm:w-auto justify-center md:justify-start">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 10v6m0 0l-3-3m3 3l3-3m2 8H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"></path></svg>
                        <span>Download Full Resume</span>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Right: Glassy Stats Card (carried over from old hero) -->
